    "This elevated noise level in measurements presents a challenge for the model in discerning the underlying patterns and relationships amongst the measured variables.",
    "Notably, we observed a particular sensitivity within the model to this measurement noise.",
    "A pathway to improving the model's performance could involve refining the speed and resolution of PIV measurements in the vicinity of the air-water interface while simultaneously increasing the PIV field of view to capture multiple wavelengths in high wind speed scenarios.",
